{"title":"hexo+obsidian=😋","uid":"3d1dfa10672de47f4f94b77a6f8c638f","slug":"hexo+obsidian=😋","date":"2025-07-31T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2025-07-26T14:59:41.462Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo+obsidian=😋.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p>有一些obsidian的插件可以提升使用hexo的便利：</p>\n<h1 id=\"Setting\"><a href=\"#Setting\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Setting\"></a>Setting</h1><h2 id=\"新建\"><a href=\"#新建\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新建\"></a>新建</h2><p>设置 - 选项 - 文件与链接 - 新建笔记存放位置<br>可以指定source目录下为指定文件夹，毕竟一般也是用obsidian编写md的，用起来比较方便。</p>\n<h2 id=\"搜索\"><a href=\"#搜索\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"搜索\"></a>搜索</h2><p>设置 - 选项 - 文件与链接 - 忽略文件<br>可以将除了source之外的所有目录都设置为忽略，这样子在obsidian中全局搜索时就不会遍历忽略目录，只会在自己编写的博客内容里搜索。</p>\n<h2 id=\"模板\"><a href=\"#模板\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"模板\"></a>模板</h2><p>设置 - 核心插件 - 模板<br>可以指定某一目录下的md文件作为模板，通过hexo+obsidian=😋，1753977600000等内容自动替换。<br>自用的是快速插入Front-Meta信息，比较方便。</p>\n<h1 id=\"Theam\"><a href=\"#Theam\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Theam\"></a>Theam</h1><p>搭配使用<a href=\"https://github.com/auroral-ui/aurora-obsidian-md\">aurora-obsidian-md: 🗒 A futuristic theme for Obsidian.md</a>相应的主题。</p>\n<h1 id=\"Plugin\"><a href=\"#Plugin\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Plugin\"></a>Plugin</h1><h2 id=\"obsidian-image-auto-upload-plugin-auto-upload-image-with-picgo\"><a href=\"#obsidian-image-auto-upload-plugin-auto-upload-image-with-picgo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"obsidian-image-auto-upload-plugin: auto upload image with picgo\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/renmu123/obsidian-image-auto-upload-plugin\">obsidian-image-auto-upload-plugin: auto upload image with picgo</a></h2><p>自动图片上传图床，味大无需多盐。</p>\n<h2 id=\"buttons-Buttons-in-Obsidian\"><a href=\"#buttons-Buttons-in-Obsidian\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"buttons: Buttons in Obsidian\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/shabegom/buttons\">buttons: Buttons in Obsidian</a></h2><p>非常全面，强大的插件。按钮样式支持自定义，支持调用 Ob 命令和其他插件命令，也可以执行 JS 脚本命令。在hexo这，我主要用于快速执行博客启动和git推送的功能，毕竟每次到博客路径下输命令也挺麻烦的。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bat\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Folder #Obsidian仓库</span><br><span class=\"line\">├── .obsidian</span><br><span class=\"line\">├── HexoBlog</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   ├── node_modules..</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   ├── public..</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   ├── scaffolds..</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   ├── source..</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   └── themes..</span><br><span class=\"line\">├── demo</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   ├── bat</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   │   ├── develop.bat</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   │   └── server.bat</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   └── Demo.<span class=\"built_in\">md</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">└── Home.<span class=\"built_in\">md</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#develop.bat</span><br><span class=\"line\">#!/bin/sh</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> ../../blog &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#server.bat</span><br><span class=\"line\">#!/bin/sh</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">start</span> http://localhost:<span class=\"number\">4000</span>/</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> ../../blog &amp;&amp; hexo c &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>通过点击按钮，快速执行命令，减少重复性劳作：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://bimg.ta0t1e.com/20250726224958291.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>其实Buttons并不是必须的，通过obsidian的添加链接与嵌入文件也是可以执行的，使用插件的主要一个原因是按钮大一点好点击。</p>\n<h2 id=\"any-block-obsidian-x2F-markdown-it-x2F-vuepress-plugin-x2F-app\"><a href=\"#any-block-obsidian-x2F-markdown-it-x2F-vuepress-plugin-x2F-app\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"any-block(obsidian&#x2F;markdown-it&#x2F;vuepress plugin&#x2F;app)\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/any-block/any-block\">any-block(obsidian&#x2F;markdown-it&#x2F;vuepress plugin&#x2F;app)</a></h2><p>支持在obsidian中对<code>markdown-it</code>插件的显示，可以实现实时阅览修改。</p>\n<h2 id=\"缺一个obsidian同步hexo双向链接的插件等我体现一下再写\"><a href=\"#缺一个obsidian同步hexo双向链接的插件等我体现一下再写\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"缺一个obsidian同步hexo双向链接的插件等我体现一下再写\"></a>缺一个obsidian同步hexo双向链接的插件等我体现一下再写</h2>","feature":false,"text":"有一些obsidian的插件可以提升使用hexo的便利： Setting新建设置 - 选项 - 文件与链接 - 新建笔记存放位置可以指定source目录下为指定...","permalink":"/post/hexo+obsidian=😋","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.3k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"helloworld","slug":"helloworld","count":2,"path":"api/categories/helloworld.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"helloworld","slug":"helloworld","count":2,"path":"api/tags/helloworld.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Setting\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Setting</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">新建</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">搜索</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF\"><span cl